3eGorgeous design\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003eAdd USB-C charging port\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003eEasy to remove\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0D3J63BWD?tag=cult087-20\" data-lasso-box-trackable=\"true\" data-lasso-id=\"882494\" data-lasso-name=\"Apple iPad Magic Keyboard Case for iPad Pro\" title=\"Apple iPad Magic Keyboard Case for iPad Pro\" rel=\"nofollow noopener sponsored\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71YMMFyaCPL._AC_SX679_.jpg\" height=\"500\" width=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Apple iPad Magic Keyboard Case for iPad Pro\"/\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003eLogitech Combo Touch\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cfigure id=\"31739\" aria-labelledby=\"figcaption_31739\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.cultofmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Logitech-Combo-Touch-iPad-Pro-keyboard-case.jpg\" data-lasso-id=\"1641669067\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" title=\"Logitech Combo Touch iPad keyboard case\" src=\"https://www.cultofmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Logitech-Combo-Touch-iPad-Pro-keyboard-case-1440x810.jpg\" alt=\"Logitech Combo Touch iPad keyboard case\" width=\"780\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https://www.cultofmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Logitech-Combo-Touch-iPad-Pro-keyboard-case-1440x810.jpg.webp 1440w, https://www.cultofmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Logitech-Combo-Touch-iPad-Pro-keyboard-case-400x225.jpg 400w, https://www.cultofmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Logitech-Combo-Touch-iPad-Pro-keyboard-case-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://www.cultofmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Logitech-Combo-Touch-iPad-Pro-keyboard-case-350x197.jpg 350w, https://www.cultofmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Logitech-Combo-Touch-iPad-Pro-keyboard-case.jpg 1602w, https://www.cultofmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Logitech-Combo-Touch-iPad-Pro-keyboard-case-400x225@2x.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"figcaption_31739\"\u003eLogitech Combo Touch is one of the best iPad keyboard cases.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePhoto: Logitech\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThose looking for an iPad keyboard case that focuses more on protecting the tablet should consider the Logitech Combo Touch. It comes in two sections so the keyboard flap can be removed while leaving the iPad in a wrap-around case. And the case portion includes a kickstand.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBuy it from:\u003c/strong\u003e Amazon\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Logitech-Combo-Touch-13-inch-Keyboard/dp/B0D3NKVVM6?tag=cult087-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-lasso-id=\"1641669068\" data-lasso-name=\"Logitech Combo Touch iPad keyboard case\"\u003e13-inch iPad Pro\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Logitech-Combo-Touch-11-inch-Keyboard/dp/B0D3NM94Y9\" data-lasso-id=\"1641669069\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e11-inch iPad Pro\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Logitech-Detachable-Precision-Full-Size-Technology/dp/B0BJYR1Z6N\" data-lasso-id=\"1641669070\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eiPad 10\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"lasso-anchor-id-885346-1641668997\"\u003e\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\tUpgrade your iPad\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Logitech-Combo-Touch-13-inch-Keyboard/dp/B0D3NKVVM6?tag=c